		"_postman_id": "csv-knowledge-base-api",
		"name": "CSV Knowledge Base API",
		"description": "Complete collection for testing the CSV Upload and Knowledge Base API with AI-powered metadata analysis.\n\n## 🚀 Features Tested\n- CSV file upload (single & multiple)\n- Document management\n- Column metadata extraction\n- AI-powered knowledge base creation\n- Search and discovery\n\n## 📋 Prerequisites\n1. Start the API server: `python main.py`\n2. Ensure environment variables are configured\n3. Have a sample CSV file ready for upload\n\n## 🔄 Recommended Test Flow\n1. Health Check\n2. Upload CSV File\n3. Extract Column Metadata\n4. Save Enriched Metadata\n5. Process with AI\n6. Query Knowledge Base\n7. Search & List Operations",
		"schema": "https://schema.getpostman.com/json/collection/v2.1.0/collection.json"
	},
